    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Non-auditory effects of noise",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 3.39,
      "endTime": 13.03
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What conclusion does the author draw about noise and health in this piece?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 13.04,
      "endTime": 20.96,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Many people in industry and the Services,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.97,
      "endTime": 24.91
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "who have practical experience of noise,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 24.92,
      "endTime": 28.1
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "regard any investigation of this question as a waste of time;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.11,
      "endTime": 33.51,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they are not prepared even to admit the possibility that noise affects people.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.52,
      "endTime": 39.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "On the other hand,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.59,
      "endTime": 41.13
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "those who dislike noise will sometimes use most inadequate evidence",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 41.14,
      "endTime": 46.04,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "to support their pleas for a quieter society.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 46.05,
      "endTime": 51.23,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This is a pity, because noise abatement really is a good cause,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.24,
      "endTime": 57.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and it is likely to be discredited if it gets to be associated with bad science.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.25,
      "endTime": 64.02,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "One allegation often made is that noise produces mental illness.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 64.03,
      "endTime": 69.77,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A recent article in a weekly newspaper, for instance,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 69.78,
      "endTime": 74.07
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "was headed with a striking illustration of a lady in a state of considerable distress,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.08,
      "endTime": 80.71
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "with the caption 'She was yet another victim, reduced to a screaming wreck'.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 80.72,
      "endTime": 88.21
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "On turning eagerly to the text, one learns that the lady was a typist",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.22,
      "endTime": 93.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "who found the sound of office typewriters worried her more and more",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 93.76,
      "endTime": 97.85,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "until eventually she had to go into a mental hospital.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 97.86,
      "endTime": 102.7
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Now the snag in this sort of anecdote is of course that one cannot distinguish cause and effect.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 102.71,
      "endTime": 110.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Was the noise a cause of the illness,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 110.45,
      "endTime": 113.17
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "or were the complaints about noise merely a symptom?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 113.18,
      "endTime": 117.47
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Another patient might equally well complain",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 117.48,
      "endTime": 120.29,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "that her neighbours were combining to slander her and persecute her,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.3,
      "endTime": 124.91,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and yet one might be cautious about believing this statement.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 124.92,
      "endTime": 129.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What is needed in the case of noise is a study of large numbers of people living under noisy conditions,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 129.74,
      "endTime": 137.16,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "to discover whether they are mentally ill more often than other people are.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 137.17,
      "endTime": 142.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Some time ago the United States Navy, for instance,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 142.66,
      "endTime": 146.75
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "examined a very large number of men working on aircraft carriers:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 146.76,
      "endTime": 151.99,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          },
          {
            "word": "Number",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "号码，数字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the study was known as Project Anehin.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 152,
      "endTime": 156.38
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It can be unpleasant to live even several miles from an aerodrome;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 156.39,
      "endTime": 161.66,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "if you think what it must be like to share the deck of a ship with several squadrons of jet aircraft,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 161.67,
      "endTime": 168.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "you will realize that a modern navy is a good place to study noise.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 168.6,
      "endTime": 174.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "You",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "你，你们"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "But neither psychiatric interviews nor objective tests",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 174.98,
      "endTime": 179.6
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "were able to show any effects upon these American sailors.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 179.61,
      "endTime": 184.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "American",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "美国的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "This result merely confirms earlier American and British studies:",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 184.41,
      "endTime": 189.98,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "American",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "美国的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s33",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "if there is any effect of noise upon mental health,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 189.99,
      "endTime": 193.89,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s34",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "it must be so small that present methods of psychiatric diagnosis cannot find it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 193.9,
      "endTime": 202.53,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s35",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "That does not prove that it does not exist; but it does mean",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 202.54,
      "endTime": 207.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s36",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "that noise is less dangerous than, say being brought up in an orphanage",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 207.73,
      "endTime": 213.71,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s37",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "--which really is a mental health hazard.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 213.72,
      "endTime": 218.72,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
